38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-choreographed-political-meet-carries-message-control-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国投资者埃利奥特放弃对英国咖喱的收购要约</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/us-investor-elliott-says-wont-make-offer-uks-currys-2024-03-11/</link><description>美国投资者 Elliott Advisors 不打算对 Currys 提出收购要约，称这家英国电器零售商的董事会不会参与其中。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 07:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/us-investor-elliott-says-wont-make-offer-uks-currys-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国通过法律赋予共产党更多对内阁的控制权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-passes-law-granting-communist-party-more-control-over-cabinet-2024-03-11/</link><description>中国人大周一修改了一项法律，在三十年来首次取消了总理的会后新闻发布会后，实际上赋予了共产党对中国内阁国务院的更多行政控制权。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 07:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-passes-law-granting-communist-party-more-control-over-cabinet-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：强调日本央行的积极因素</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-03-11/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 05:32:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国监管部门要求大型银行加大对万科的支持力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-regulators-ask-large-banks-step-up-support-vanke-sources-say-2024-03-11/</link><description>两位消息人士称，中国已要求银行加强对国家支持的万科的融资支持，并呼吁债权人考虑延长私人债务期限，这是中央政府为帮助陷入困境的房地产公司进行的罕见干预。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-regulators-ask-large-banks-step-up-support-vanke-sources-say-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国试图使台湾附近的军事演习“正常化”：岛内最高安全官员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-trying-normalise-military-drills-near-taiwan-islands-top-security-official-2024-03-11/</link><description>台湾最高安全官员周一向国会表示，中国平均每 7 至 10 天在台湾附近进行一次“联合战备巡逻”，称中国军队正试图使台湾附近的演习“正常化”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 02:48:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-trying-normalise-military-drills-near-taiwan-islands-top-security-official-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国大使称在中国被判处死刑的澳大利亚作家可能永远不会被执行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-writer-sentenced-death-china-may-never-be-executed-says-chinese-2024-03-11/</link><description>中国驻澳大利亚大使周一表示，如果这位前民主博主不再犯下任何罪行，上个月对被监禁的澳大利亚作家杨恒均判处的死刑缓期执行可能不会执行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 02:38:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-writer-sentenced-death-china-may-never-be-executed-says-chinese-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>中东战争抵消了对中国需求的担忧，油价稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-fall-china-demand-worries-2024-03-11/</link><description>由于中东和俄罗斯持续存在的地缘政治担忧与对中国需求疲软的担忧相互冲突，全球基准布伦特原油价格周一保持稳定，徘徊在每桶 82 美元左右。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:56:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-fall-china-demand-worries-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>韩国监管机构发现中国股票衍生品销售存在不当行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-watchdog-finds-wrongdoings-sales-china-equity-derivatives-2024-03-11/</link><description>韩国金融市场监管机构周一表示，发现销售与香港股市指数挂钩的衍生品的金融公司存在不当行为。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-watchdog-finds-wrongdoings-sales-china-equity-derivatives-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国大使称澳大利亚葡萄酒关税审查已步入正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-ambassador-says-review-into-tariffs-australian-wine-progressing-well-2024-03-11/</link><description>中国大使肖千周一表示，中国对澳大利亚葡萄酒关税的审查进展顺利，但他没有证实澳大利亚政府声称争端将于本月得到解决。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 00:32:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-ambassador-says-review-into-tariffs-australian-wine-progressing-well-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>随着不确定性的蔓延，欧洲股市从历史高位回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-11/</link><description>欧洲股指周一早盘大多下跌，从上周的历史高位回落，因交易员努力应对经济前景的不确定性，并等待本周晚些时候的美国通胀数据。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 00:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：中国的通胀、资本流动趋势正在逆转吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-10/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 22:43:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>